{"tid":2427727,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《第九禁區》導演 Neill Blomkamp 證實續集《第十禁區》正在開發中","createTime":"2021-03-01T04:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T10:54:22.000Z","uid":149201,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"376d27c0d726c7ddab5e1501813946907607ecc8","tid":2427727,"uid":149201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:16:53.000Z","msg":"如要說到 2000 年後的科幻新銳導演，不得不提曾被指望接續《Alien》系列但卻無疾而終的導演 Neill Blomkamp，在 2009 年推出成本僅僅 $3,000 萬美金，卻在全球斬獲破 $2 億美金票房，並成為科幻電影史蔚為經典的《District 9》（第九禁區/D-9異形禁區）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十年過去了，Neill Blomkamp 突然於本週於宣佈《District 9》最新續集《District 10》的劇本正在開發中，共同編劇包括《District 9》男主角 Sharlto Copley 與妻子 Terri Tatchell  兩人，並說道：「 Its coming&hellip;」，而關於上映日期、卡司等情報仍未公布，不過此消息一出絕對是眾多科幻迷心中的好消息，Neill Blomkamp 對於科幻的執著與創作能力可說是大眾有目共睹，有興趣的讀者們敬請留意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2021/2/neill-blomkamp-district-9-sequl-district-10-in-the-works\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2021%2F2%2Fneill-blomkamp-district-9-sequl-district-10-in-the-works&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3bsYlYTGbxuQQGsxDmAgPG8%3D&h=cbce0e54\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2021/2/neill-blomkamp-district-9-sequl-district-10-in-the-works</a><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/SQ5C.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2FSQ5C.gif&h=5627ed04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee51a41b9bfd559f8b67d011cc493a88d0693d08","tid":2427727,"uid":152331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:19:12.000Z","msg":"係咪1個人斷左隻手 駁左隻外星人手 跟住慢慢變外星人個套"},{"pid":"15cf1c9d6ac3a999930bce42ca38d00005ac8091","tid":2427727,"uid":18337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望係接返上一集"},{"pid":"b69f35c5dfdf67030df6d118d3b32b96a02c7c49","tid":2427727,"uid":27126,"like":0,"di